DEFINITIONS

"NLPSSC" refers to the Natural Language Processing Support Services Core, an academic research core facility.

"Software" refers to the computer program(s), source code, documentation, and any associated materials distributed under this license.

"Academic Institution" refers to a university, college, research institute, or other non-profit educational or research organization.

"Non-Commercial Academic Research" refers to research activities conducted by Academic Institutions for educational or scientific purposes that do not involve direct commercial gain or the development of commercial products or services.

PURPOSE

This software is developed to support academic research in the field of natural language processing and is intended for use by researchers affiliated with Academic Institutions for Non-Commercial Academic Research purposes only.

